OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Fsome wintry, will continue overnight,
OL,7,Fespecially in the far north, and
OL,8,Facross Wales, central and later
OL,9,Fsouthern parts of England. Otherwise
OL,10,Fclear periods will develop and the
OL,11,Fstrong and gusty northwesterly wind
OL,12,Fwill ease. Turning frosty with icy
OL,13,Fpatches.
OL,14,
OL,15,CThursday:FThursday will start mostly
OL,16,Ffine with some sunshine. It will
OL,17,Fgradually turn cloudy, wet and breezy
OL,18,Fin the north. Meanwhile, much of
OL,19,FEngland and Wales will remain dry and
OL,20,Fbright.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
